==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lifter
<hw>Lift"er</hw> <pr>(l⟦icr⟧ft"⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who, or that which, lifts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Founding)</fld> <def>A tool for lifting loose sand
from the mold; also, a contrivance attached to a cope, to hold the sand
together when the cope is lifted.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lifting</ent>⟦br⟧
